  {
    "content_id": 419548,
    "reference_id": 109147,
    "title": "Hesabu 9:1–10:36",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "04009001-04010036",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Makuhani walipaswa kupiga <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108386\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">tarumbeta</span> za fedha ili kuwapa Waisraeli ujumbe.</p><p>Mungu alisema kwamba sauti hiyo ingemkumbusha kuhusu Waisraeli. Hii haikumaanisha kwamba Mungu wakati mwingine aliwasahau. Hii ilikuwa njia ya kuelezea jinsi Mungu anavyowajali watu wake (<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108302\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">watu wa Mungu</span>). Yeye huwatunza kila wakati. Hata husikiliza kelele wanazotoa.</p><p>Kabla ya kuondoka jangwani karibu na Mlima Sinai, Waisraeli walisherehekea tena <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108317\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">Sikukuu ya Pasaka</span>.</p><p><span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108369\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">Wageni</span> kama <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108387\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">Hobabu</span> wangeweza kushiriki katika karamu (<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108372\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">karamu</span>) ikiwa walitaka.</p><p>Kisha makabila yaliondoka Sinai. Walimtii Mungu kabisa kwa kuondoka kambini kwa utaratibu ambao Mungu aliwaambia. Ishara ya kufanya hivi ilikuwa ni wakati wingu juu ya hema takatifu liliposonga.</p>",
